<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/2006/559739.jpg" alt="#YouthMonth: Kgabo Legodi believes access to the internet is the biggest challenge" width="600" height="311">Kgabo Legodi, a communication and education enthusiast from Polokwane, Limpopo Province, believes that one of the biggest issues youth face today is the access to the internet.Kgabo, who runs her own PR company in her community, shares her views in this video.